ALGORITHM

1.	Start
2.	Initialize DPTR to 4700H
3.	Read the number from memory location 4700H and store it in B register
4.	Increment DPTR and read the value from next memory location and store it to accumulator
5.	Divide the accumulator by B register and store the result to the accumulator and B register
6.	Increment DPTR and store the quotient to memory location 4702H
7.	Increment DPTR and store the remainder to memory location 4703H
8.	Stop

