PROCEDURE

•	Step 1: Power ON the 8051 Trainer Kit.
•	Step 2: Enter the program by selecting the A (Address) option and specifying the starting address 4100.
•	Step 3: Enter the input using SP (Store Program) starting from the addresses 4700.
•	Step 4: Execute the program using the GO command followed by the program’s starting address.
•	Step 5: Verify the output using SP (Store Program) starting from the addresses 4702.

